{"tid":744664,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"老老實實...我覺得利記下季真係好大機會拎到英超","createTime":"2018-07-16T06:13:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T08:22:52.000Z","uid":31314,"like":48,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"306554bd2351144045eb1bc0ab54210d9252f6a3","tid":744664,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:13:48.000Z","msg":"個人覺得今屆係好有機會拿冠軍的一年~比去年更大機會~<br />\n簡單分析幾個主要對手~<br />\n<br />\n曼聯~~今年走了卡域克其實佢地實力削弱了好多~<br />\n先講陣容~羅美路傷了~全能到仆街開始老了同輕敵~迪基亞世界杯失了好多波~<br />\n中前場無了朗尼的曼聯已經無以前咁大殺傷力~我吾信馬迪同靴里拉可以頂得著咁密賽程~<br />\n單單依賴一個普巴係吾足夠~個人認為盧卡古同拉車福特幫助不大~<br />\n<br />\n車仔~~佢D主將星散~<br />\n夏世三, 高圖爾斯,金章安~<br />\n剩低班人可不可以頂住呢D賽程係一個大問題~~<br />\n同個人覺得沙里吾係一個咁有料的人~有幾多個好似魔佬咁勁~<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴~冇左雲加既阿仙奴已經不值一提~<br />\n<br />\n曼城~~雖然佢地大把錢買人~但係都要磨合的~同埋哥迪奧拿都係一般般~暫時沒有機會冧莊~<br />\n<br />\n至於利物浦今年雖然走了安尼簡~但一支球隊吾會話走左一個人就會差成咁~<br />\n個人覺得沙b攻擊力比安尼簡更好~(不喜物插)~有待時間証明~<br />\n今屆無可否認比以往差左~但我寧願今季差D~下季慢慢追上來~<br />\n無記錯~都已買左3個人~今屆好明顯高普爸B比過去更重視聯賽~<br />\n希望下季可以殺低曼城~一鼓作氣過埋曼聯呢關~<br />\n保持氣勢到季尾<br />\n各位巴打一條心支持利記今屆奪首個英超~~"},{"pid":"9e3a543261df2947dcedd628e2f0952db58e6644","tid":744664,"uid":9891,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:19:39.000Z","msg":"屌你老母~"},{"pid":"90aa6ba54d2c0eb0f23a59060f7d12e77412dd3d","tid":744664,"uid":48521,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:21:17.000Z","msg":"樓主驚到晨咁早未開咧就要燈到先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9418f77ce8c02d7f22d0c56b022920a39c761c83","tid":744664,"uid":154664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:21:40.000Z","msg":"利你老母"},{"pid":"0c4a7223a4a6e022f16c2beb09e10f64273993a2","tid":744664,"uid":2756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:33:08.000Z","msg":"熱狗呢"},{"pid":"03d2bbd26c6f7760b8e07575dc4599796dc87ae9","tid":744664,"uid":194525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:37:05.000Z","msg":"梗係猁攞第一啦 人地有世界第一中堅喎 啲前鋒見到佢都嚇到賴尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad6bd77cc2a92d8c43a06840b66c65e8071f4f54","tid":744664,"uid":32486,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:38:33.000Z","msg":"留意到英超各隊都好怕利物浦拎冠<br />\n一早開 post 燈定先<br />\n連洛夫雲都要開 post 講係我利唯一奪冠球員<br />\n點解唔講下普巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4297cc631fb77a0bc3fed672853d1cf9e8c5c82","tid":744664,"uid":47164,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:38:43.000Z","msg":"傻尻獌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9228bfd9810a2da38d1c8b03d4fa663d6e723b6e","tid":744664,"uid":36811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:41:22.000Z","msg":"ching sick ball <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d57a0aa40b93cc48559c7d868f7c2af2069388","tid":744664,"uid":91502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:45:13.000Z","msg":"你當我未來熱死嫁？"},{"pid":"c9e4ec523f158951924a0eacc84438c5f1297d07","tid":744664,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:46:08.000Z","msg":"見證新潮文誕生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a160d1834ce3594da9ea6742a4f3a8519d9c4b4","tid":744664,"uid":61853,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:48:30.000Z","msg":"朝早起身: J 艾加紋身圖 <br />\n早餐食紅雞蛋，一條心，撐紅軍！ <br />\n睇番歐聯05奪冠珍藏版dvd，拎定三卷tempo廁紙，以防睇到射12碼階段走火 <br />\n<br />\nlunch食海鮮 <br />\n慶祝今季脫離海鮮足球，食一餐贏一場，聯賽38連勝指日可待 <br />\n<br />\n下午gel頭扮軒達臣，開電腦J謝拉特/加歷查/杜格利殊 <br />\n<br />\nJ完換利物浦(作客)波衫落街，買支嘉士柏(前利物浦sponsor)，飲到扯扯地。 <br />\n<br />\n晚飯係全日重點，著住全套利記波衫波褲，手持you will never walk alone頸巾，去49000餐廳舊地址，大唱會歌共5555次，5字=5次歐聯冠軍。 <br />\n<br />\n晚上安然跳上利物浦床單睡床，準備夢見全隊利物浦職球員夢遺！"},{"pid":"585a132f70800e5c9ed784b1657b0542ab5f104a","tid":744664,"uid":34996,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:57:24.000Z","msg":"吾你老母"},{"pid":"15f7390d6763ab4b34474dc545c627564da089ba","tid":744664,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:58:09.000Z","msg":"沙基猁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4068f5ccaa9a758d667f1eb0faeb1bbd07ecccb","tid":744664,"uid":88110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:03:58.000Z","msg":"今季咁早開工"},{"pid":"93f487d14ff3d432b4a6680948505de6e381bc7b","tid":744664,"uid":142314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:13:08.000Z","msg":"曼瘕上年冠左仲要磨合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f378053757dd1c436fa105b66a661fde1489a8e7","tid":744664,"uid":115150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:30:52.000Z","msg":"獌都算主要對手？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f92f9848601d44e1c8f67085ed7184a9dda83d","tid":744664,"uid":2033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:38:08.000Z","msg":"樓豬死猁狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a062393623567e988731652c5bc00f2d363a314a","tid":744664,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44f92f9848601d44e1c8f67085ed7184a9dda83d","tid":744664,"uid":2033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:38:08.000Z","msg":"樓豬死猁狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:46:23.000Z","msg":"下季神軒雙殺你班死獌狗！"},{"pid":"05a53126930efc1bcb5a294b5b169e405d945ccb","tid":744664,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90aa6ba54d2c0eb0f23a59060f7d12e77412dd3d","tid":744664,"uid":48521,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:21:17.000Z","msg":"樓主